Adding Total sales KPI 18


Total Sales




1. Copy and paste the ‘Total Active Customers’ KPI card.
2. Uncheck the ‘Total Active Customers’ and select or drag the ‘Total Sales’ measure to the Fields section
3. Make the following changes:
General:
Height=114
Width=216
Position =>
Horizontal=1
Vertical=407
Title=On, Text= Total Sales
Font=Segoe UI (12)
Text color=#FFFFFF
Background color=#094780
Horizontal alignment=Center
Effects =>
Background=On
Background color=#F1F7F6
Transparency=0%
Visual boarder=on
Visual:
Callout Value =>
Font=Segoe UI Semibold (40)
Font color=#e1c233
Category label=Off
